Checkout the repository in /usr/local/src/ and this
script and service will work fine.

vaderbot.sh - /usr/local/bin/vaderbot.sh
- pulls from upstream
- starts the bot

If on a system using systemd:

vaderbot.service - /etc/systemd/system/vaderbot.service
- systemctl enable vaderbot.service (make it run at startup)
- systemctl start vaderbot.service
- systemctl restart vaderbot.service
- systemct status vaderbot.service

If on a system using upstart:

vaderbot.conf - /etc/init/vaderbot.conf
- start vaderbot
- stop vaderbot
- status vaderbot
- restart vaderbot
